{"tid":1123747,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【誤殺親夫】美國丈夫偷訂色情頻道 太太發現後向其腳開兩槍","createTime":"2019-04-24T15:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T10:00:06.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e195ae1697c3ffe4f8d8298493274bf6499c919e","tid":1123747,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"美國阿肯色州一名婦人發現丈夫訂閱衞星電視的色情頻道，怒火中燒，取出手槍開兩槍，將丈夫擊斃，陪審團周二判她二級誤殺罪成。<br />\n<br />\n69歲婦人帕特里夏（Patricia Hill）被控於去年7月，在家中槍殺65歲丈夫希爾（Frank Hill），她作供指，自己之前曾取消訂閱衞星電視的色情頻道，但當她查看賬單時，發現希爾又偷偷訂閱色情頻道，因而朝丈夫的腳開兩槍，但懷疑當時希爾彎下腰致傷勢嚴重。帕特里夏之後打電話報警，希爾送院後不治。<br />\n<br />\n她在庭上堅稱，自己開槍只是希望得到對方的注意，沒想過演變成殺死他。她的代表律師指，兩夫婦感情已經轉淡，但帕特里夏認為丈夫看色情影片是「侮辱她與上帝」，「她向他說了一遍又一遍要求他停止，他稱自己會停的，但最後再犯&hellip;&hellip;她失去了理智」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190424/59523332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190424%2F59523332&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0qy4iG8TIfC1p449sO1N5Ck%3D&h=7f6583e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190424%2F59523332&h=95129868\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190424/59523332</a>"},{"pid":"d3e10bcff23e00b138998050ab631c41e59bdbca","tid":1123747,"uid":79744,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:49:41.000Z","msg":"誤殺？<br />\n如果調轉係個老公殺老婆會點判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc92d4a46680b6ef37bd40019fd2eeedfa121b3","tid":1123747,"uid":124372,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:54:39.000Z","msg":"睇av都要死"},{"pid":"3e43b5be941e8830c40b3386c99dadf6fdd1cb5e","tid":1123747,"uid":42340,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:55:22.000Z","msg":"其實毒撚一個更開心....."},{"pid":"72ff837157f02c8fe8c826187a5cfdc651b8858d","tid":1123747